      <title>罗伯茨推迟了特朗普的司法弹each电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-escalates-fight-with-courts-by-calling-for-impeachment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席大法官约翰·罗伯茨（John Roberts）反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统呼吁弹each法官的呼吁，该法官裁定反对迅速驱逐委内瑞拉帮派成员的努力。]]></description>
