    <item>
      <title>智利中央总统竞争者希望减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/chile-center-right-presidential-contender-wants-business-tax-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利中央总统候选人伊芙琳·马特雷斯（Evelyn Matthei）表示，由于她的竞选活动试图在今年的大选中保持其领先者地位，因此她想将该国的公司税率从27％削减到18％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/chile-center-right-presidential-contender-wants-business-tax-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 15:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的地标支出狂欢赢得议会批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-pass-landmark-spending-package-ending-era-of-budget-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国立法者通过了一个具有里程碑意义的支出计划，朝着为国防和基础设施的债务融资付出了数千亿欧元的重大一步，并在预算紧缩的几十年结束时预示着。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-pass-landmark-spending-package-ending-era-of-budget-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 15:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚比索在未经证实的Guevara退出报告中潜入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/colombia-peso-slides-on-reports-finance-minister-stepping-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的债券和货币周二在未经证实的当地媒体报道中跌倒了，该报告称，该国财政部长迭戈·格瓦拉（Diego Guevara）将在短短三个月的职位上下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/colombia-peso-slides-on-reports-finance-minister-stepping-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 13:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京希望乌克兰的所有武器因特朗普休战而停止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/putin-is-said-to-want-all-arms-to-ukraine-halted-for-trump-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）要求在美国对方唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提议的停火期间停用所有武器向乌克兰运送。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/putin-is-said-to-want-all-arms-to-ukraine-halted-for-trump-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 10:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼在退出政治竞选之前持有680万美元的布鲁克菲尔德选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/carney-held-6-8-million-of-brookfield-options-before-quitting-for-political-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）在布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司（Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.）持有股票期权，截至12月底，其价值680万美元，但投资经理的年度10-K申请几乎没有提供有关付给现在加拿大总理的男子多少的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/carney-held-6-8-million-of-brookfield-options-before-quitting-for-political-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 01:48:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
